rows.label: tlk46320171_03_msg0001
rows.name:
The ration distribution service is
only available during the daytime.

rows.label: tlk46320171_03_msg0002
rows.name:
We've been trying to convince the
better-off refugees to emigrate to other
nations, but none of them are budging.

rows.label: tlk46320171_03_msg0003
rows.name:
With our limited resources, it will be
difficult to keep supporting them all
indefinitely...
